				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: FM tricks...<a name="18778"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 3 04 1:24 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>In hard LDON missions, mez lands much more reliably than lull does.  So, a very simple way to split multiple mobs is the mez-fade.  Let's say there is a room with three mobs all in agro range of each other.  Mez one, bring the other two out to your group, fade to lose agro on the mezzed mob, then mez one of the two you pulled.  The room is split nicely.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
