				<td colspan="2"><span>One trick I've learned is to deliberately get yourself summoned somewhere. Say for some odd reason you wanna get summoned up to the plateau in PoN. Step one: Charm a banshee (they summon) Step two: Target a nightmare on the plateau (or be stupid like me and target vakhsiz &lt;spelling?&gt<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-5.gif" border="0" alt="Wink" hspace="2" />and tell your pet to attack. Step three: wait for your pet to take some damage and then break charm. Once you get summoned &lt;and stunned and killed if you attacked Vhaksiz&gt; then run away a bit and use your fading memories. BINGO you are all alone on the plateau in PoN, and didn't have to run through the tunnels! Now what you are gonna do once you are up there is anyones guess, but at least you did it.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
