				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: FM tricks...<a name="19118"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 4 04 4:44 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>If you have much Flowing Thought =) Fading Memo is a way to Invis :P
<br />

<br />
Also its nice if you want to go afk somewhere where invis is nice - and are too lazy to mem invis song :P
<br />

<br />
Pulling with Fading :
<br />

<br />
2 Mobs who cant be lulled ? Mezz one pull second and Fade.
<br />

<br />
2 Mobs agroed but arent mezzable ? Song of the Highsun is your friend =) then Fade
<br />

<br />
Lull resist ? Fade - HINT : If you got a lull resist but got some place to run - Lull again before Fade till its lulled - then fade and attack second - tada no lull needed then, as lull before Fade is still working.
<br />

<br />
Sometimes you got mobs which cant be lulled mezzed etc. but like to Run faster than the adds =)
<br />
For example : Rumblecrush in Umbral Planes =)
<br />
Agro em, run run run till RC is near but his friends are far - Fade - agro RC again =) There you got him solo.
<br />

<br />
Want to camp something deep in a dungeon ?
<br />
For example : Neriad Shawl in Sirens Grotto :
<br />
SoW is very useful too, but sirens in this situation is awesome, because fishes wont follow you on landside.
<br />
Anyway : Move in - Divine Aura Song - Run Run Run - Fade at spot =)
<br />

<br />
-------------
<br />

<br />
Fading Memories Really Saves Lifes.
<br />
In a huge swarm kite but no zone close to you ? Fade =)
<br />

<br />
Rampage ? Fade
<br />

<br />
Main Agro o_O ? Fade
<br />

<br />
Agroed wrong mob ? Fade
<br />

<br />
etc.
<br />

<br />
All i can say : This is the BEST AA bards get. I cant imagine any other which should be better =)</span></td>
